<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Persbel to seek freedom from Dagbreek Trust.</title>
<headline>Persbel to seek freedom from Dagbreek Trust.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Perskor Beleggings Ltd said on Friday a meeting would be convened in June by order of the High Court of South Africa to obtain the relinquishment of control by The Dagbreek Trust and consider its compensation.</p>
<p>Persbel will propose that the 33,000 extraordinary Persbel shares held by Dagbreek be converted to 1.63 million Persbel ordinary shares.</p>
<p>The meeting will be held on June 18.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27 11 482 1003</p>
